items.name: SCHOOL，学校模型ZSschoolV1.0
items.description:
8K+高清建筑学校

简介：这是一款专为绘制建筑外立面的LoRA模型，基于SDXL底模制作，其风格偏向效果图和写实，拥有非常真实光影，是一款非常精致的建筑模型。是建筑系列中的学校的外立面。推荐搭配模型sdXL_v1.0使用。

关于TAG:

不太建议写非常复杂的词，可以多谢一些质量词，例如masterpiece,best quality等等，不知道怎么写可以直接复制下面的提示词：

(masterpiece), best quality,8K,no humans, outdoors,xuexiao,school,building, scenery,blue sky, (stairs:0.7),grass, day,tree,window,

负面：“lowres, bad anatomy, text, error, extra digit, fewer digits,cropped, worst quality, low quality, normal quality, jpeg artifacts, signature,watermark, username, blurry”

触发词：xuexiao(必写）, school（非必写）

权重：0.4-0.6（推荐0.5，根据尺寸比例调整）

关于参数设置:

迭代步数：30-100（过于低的步数可能会导致画面扭曲）

采样方法：Euler a、DPM、SDE

放大算法：4x-UltraSharp/R-ESRGAN 4X+

放大倍数：1.5-2.0倍

重绘幅度：0.1-0.3

推荐尺寸：1536x1024、1024x1536，不同尺寸需采用不同的权重（如果要开高分辨率修复的话，显卡至少24G以上）

CFG Scale：6.5-8.5（推荐使用默认的7即可）

如果高清修复要炸显存，建议通过后期处理放大，或者通过其他工具进行精修！

It is not recommended to write very complex words, you can thank some quality words, such as masterpiece, best quality, etc., if you don't know how to write, you can directly copy the following prompt words:

(masterpiece), best quality,8K,no humans, outdoors,xuexiao,school,building, scenery,blue sky, (stairs:0.7),grass, day,tree,window,

为什么已经有了这么多黑丝LORA，还要再做一个？因为我发现：

1、现有的LORA都会对画面产生一些污染。要不然是衣服，要不然是鞋，要不然是身材。可否做一个LORA，只会对黑丝的质感产生影响，而不会对其他画面内容产生影响？

So I made this LORA, and later I will make a series of LORAs with different thicknesses and textures, all of which are made of real-life materials and made using the difference extraction method to ensure the quality.

1. Make sure you use LORA correctly.

5. Don't add too much negative, otherwise it will affect the effect of LORA.

8. The large models currently tried are relatively good, such as the Moyou series and the Maiju series, which seem to be more friendly to real-life models. For different large models, parameters need to be adjusted.
